Hey there ✨
 
It's been a while! 🌌 Deta Space team here.
 
For the past ~1.5 years, Deta has been working on building Surf - a desktop app that brings your files and the web directly into
your stream of thoughts.

Yesterday, Surf went Open Source! 👾 🫶

Here's the Github repo [https://github.com/deta/surf] - have a look ✨ Visit the site here [https://deta.surf/] ✨

Surf was inspired by the ideas in Deta Space, such as creating applets & working in one place across private & open data.
 
Thanks everyone,
 
💖💜
 
~
🌊🌊🌊
Team Deta
 
